{"tid":622944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Tim Cook：iPhone很多組件均產自美國","createTime":"2018-04-09T14:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T04:41:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a273117c5c4d452fb245f321465d9cdeac560573","tid":622944,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"近日，蘋果公司首席執行官庫克接受了外國媒體的採訪，就iPhone生產發表了看法<br />\n<br />\n庫克表示，iPhone的<span style=\"color: red;\">組件是在美國製造的。玻璃來自肯塔基州，微型芯片來自美國各州。用來生產製造的設備也遍佈美國。iPhone X上非常精細的Face ID模塊也將在美國製造</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不同的地方會有各種工廠。蘋果在這些工廠生產製造iPhone的組件。人們僅關注的是最後成品的組裝。<br />\n<br />\n所以，他們會說，成品不是在美國組裝的。但是在全球化的世界中，越來越多地開始在不同的國家做不同的事情，在某個地方獲得某個組件，在其他地方獲取其他組件，然後又在另外的地方組裝。最後這些產品走向全球各個市場。這才是全球系統的運作方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/354564.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fiphone%2F354564.htm&d=4dxi23YR79Ul%2FUsxr1Stjp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=171cf072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/iphone/354564.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e0b0e1999c09f3701a6efe8be339b338c1b09f1d","tid":622944,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a387699279aaacd2e6432df17af07a9eba1a0c57","tid":622944,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9c5830af2799a37b7a647f3446d849aa909900","tid":622944,"uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"點解蘋果唔直頭係美國組裝埋<br />\n咪可以唔駛再受中國劣質生產囉"},{"pid":"bf0f3d4c85d0a815